description: Produces an internal U.S. litigation e-discovery status summary covering ESI collection, processing, search term hits, review throughput, relevance/privilege rates, and completion forecasts. Use during discovery to brief counsel, case managers, or clients on progress, risks, and resource needs; trigger keywords: e-discovery, ESI, collection log, processing report, data load summary, review statistics, coding report, search term results, privilege review, status report.
